{"tid":1516287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【記錄】各和平集會及遊行申請人 相繼受恐嚇","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T18:40:50.000Z","uid":25178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2104f554a818e7e56ef0dad341200456698771f7","tid":1516287,"uid":25178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>集會及遊行申請人劉頴匡</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>劉頴匡家門遭淋紅油 收恐嚇訊息</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lau-18_VTOgP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flau-18_VTOgP_1200x0.png&h=1ec6bf33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/29/wEb30q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F29%2FwEb30q.jpg&h=0a3257f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/29/YzQ6dD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F29%2FYzQ6dD.jpg&h=902512fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066418&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=3d692689\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066418&h=222c5fca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066418</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>劉頴匡及糾察和義工等人等人新屋嶺拘留中心<span style=\"color: red;\">關押46小時</span></strong><br />\n「明知我們是合法遊行的主辦方和義工，身上只有遊行物資，沒有任何攻擊性武器，照樣扣留46小時，依然是無法無天。<br />\n<br />\n明明可以在觀塘警署保釋，偏偏要沒有解釋理由下送到新屋嶺，依然是不可理喻。<br />\n<br />\n明明沒有做錯任何事，都要沒收大量遊行物資，都要沒收所有人的手提電話，逐個上門搜屋，不知道想查些甚麼，依然是匪夷所思。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lauwinghong/posts/10218711953642567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flauwinghong%2Fposts%2F10218711953642567&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=3b1ac0b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lauwinghong/posts/10218711953642567</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>元朗遊行申請人鍾健平</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>踢保後警署附近遇襲 手臂嚴重受傷 記者同被毆</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chung-17_S7S4Y_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchung-17_S7S4Y_1200x0.png&h=e417a6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/tmhk-元朗遊行申請人鍾健平-踢保後警署附近遇襲-手臂嚴重受傷-記者同被毆/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftmhk-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%8D%BE%E5%81%A5%E5%B9%B3-%E8%B8%A2%E4%BF%9D%E5%BE%8C%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%86%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=a2d2da6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftmhk-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%8D%BE%E5%81%A5%E5%B9%B3-%E8%B8%A2%E4%BF%9D%E5%BE%8C%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%86%2F&h=5e778b82\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/tmhk-元朗遊行申請人鍾健平-踢保後警署附近遇襲-手臂嚴重受傷-記者同被毆/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>鍾健平<span style=\"color: red;\">拘捕折騰47小時</span>保釋後疑遭跟蹤 三改控罪 載有案件資料的密封<span style=\"color: red;\">證物袋被打開</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20190802/480pix/1564743624_61cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20190802%2F480pix%2F1564743624_61cd.jpg&h=e1a3826c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/7/1564544228_m9-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F7%2F1564544228_m9-1280w.png&h=f3a62fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「光復元朗」行動發起人鍾健平前日（28日）被警方以「組織未經批准集結」的罪名拘捕，原訂昨晚獲准以1,000元自簽保釋，但負責案件的新界北區重案組臨時反口。直至今早11時、即被拘留47小時後，鍾再收到警方通知，維持原定的保釋條件。鍾健平指，即使只等待多1小時，便屆滿48小時的拘留上限，但諮詢法律意見後，決定不「踢保」、接受保釋，下月29日下午3時往大埔警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n鍾健平友人早前向傳媒透露，鍾在保釋期間，發現放置其重要私人財物的密封證物袋，曾被人打開，袋中原載有其手機和辯護律師的其他案件資料，擬向廉政公署舉報，有人公職人員行為失當，鍾指現階段不便回應。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190730/59878283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190730%2F59878283&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=df445970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190730%2F59878283&h=b1dd2085\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190730/59878283</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>民陣召集人岑子杰</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>民陣岑子杰與友人遇襲 遭兩蒙面漢持壘球棍鐵通攻擊 友人受傷送院</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/jimmy-07_4Xa49_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjimmy-07_4Xa49_1200x0.png&h=d9921e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/岑子杰與友人遭壘球棍-鐵通襲擊-友人手臂受傷-送院治理/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0%E8%88%87%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E5%A3%98%E7%90%83%E6%A3%8D-%E9%90%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=0ad91ab3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0%E8%88%87%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E5%A3%98%E7%90%83%E6%A3%8D-%E9%90%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86%2F&h=9569d53a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/岑子杰與友人遭壘球棍-鐵通襲擊-友人手臂受傷-送院治理/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>北區水貨關注組召集人梁金成</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n「光復上水」梁金成遭藤條漢圍毆 被警告「唔好再搞事」<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-assult-08192019061949.html/hk-assult1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-assult-08192019061949.html%2Fhk-assult1.png&h=ff32b45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/hurt-03_FbjYs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhurt-03_FbjYs_1200x0.png&h=8a439a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/光復上水-梁金成遭藤條漢圍毆-被警告-唔好再搞事/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4-%E6%A2%81%E9%87%91%E6%88%90%E9%81%AD%E8%97%A4%E6%A2%9D%E6%BC%A2%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E5%86%8D%E6%90%9E%E4%BA%8B%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=5b659579\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4-%E6%A2%81%E9%87%91%E6%88%90%E9%81%AD%E8%97%A4%E6%A2%9D%E6%BC%A2%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E5%86%8D%E6%90%9E%E4%BA%8B%2F&h=edcc46f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/光復上水-梁金成遭藤條漢圍毆-被警告-唔好再搞事/</a>"},{"pid":"13e6d9cd05ea6cfb7a012edf16bf294c354b6612","tid":1516287,"uid":231818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"53993094eeeae23aee79509c96f24e35a8c3777d","tid":1516287,"uid":156666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>反欺凌<br />\n保護警察兒女 你我有責</strong></span><br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n各位中小學生 為左反欺凌 保護警察兒女<br />\n如果有確鑿證據證明邊位同學老豆老母係警察既話記得要<br />\n1.搵人放佢大頭相上黎<br />\n2.寫埋住邊區<br />\n3.寫埋讀咩學校<br />\n等市民可以隨時留意住佢地有冇比人欺凌 係有需要既時候可以保護佢地<br />\n<br />\n因為欺凌係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔局限係校園</span></span>架<br />\n而家市民咁仇警 有人可能會作出自然反應係街上做小動作搞警察兒女<br />\n例如:<br />\n1.唔小心撞佢出馬路<br />\n2.警察兒衝紅燈個陣唔小心女擋住佢唔比佢上行人路<br />\n3.唔小心踼/撞佢落樓梯<br />\n4.係街拍蚊個陣唔小心打中佢<br />\n5.係巴士唔小心擋住佢唔比佢落車<br />\n6.係巴士/小巴唔小心唔讓開比佢入去靠窗位坐<br />\n7.係巴士/小巴唔小心唔讓開比佢離開個靠窗位<br />\n8.係行人路/過馬路個陣唔小心&quot;KICK&quot;跌佢<br />\n9.唔小心擋住LIP口唔比佢入升降機<br />\n10.警察兒女趕返學搭LIP個陣 唔小心撳哂咁多層<br />\n11.係佢要上車/追車個陣唔小心扮健身撚當街捉住佢扮SALE野唔比佢走 <br />\n12.係街上唔小心撞佢落花槽<br />\n13.唔小心撞佢部手機落地<br />\n14.唔小心撞佢手上拎住既其他野落地<br />\n15.唔小心倒瀉野食/野飲落佢地件校服到<br />\n16.唔小心倒瀉野食/野飲「入」佢地個書包到<br />\n17.係鋪頭入面唔小心放左啲未比錢既野入佢個袋到<br />\n18.係佢行過個陣唔小心屋企倒屎水/污糟水落樓<br />\n19.唔小心打開佢書包拉鍊 等佢啲野跌哂出黎<br />\n20.唔小心放啲蛇蟲鼠蟻入佢書包 <br />\nETC.<br />\n<br />\n大家見到有人咁人既話記得要保護佢地 就算啲警察兒女幾忙幾趕時間都要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉住佢地</span></span>幫佢地報警 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比佢地走</span></span><br />\n你地知香港警察做野幾有效率架啦 一個人日日等幾次39分鐘<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都唔係好嘥時間姐</span></span><br />\n如果佢地自己打電話想搵人幫手 千祈唔好唔小心轟佢部手機落地然後踢到母雷公咁遠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516112/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516112/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516100/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516100/page/1?post=2</a>"},{"pid":"65f7ca5678560733d8af4483e2dc88c336c7bd43","tid":1516287,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56037201aa5dcd7b1c9bf2dd567497df06389d6d","tid":1516287,"uid":25178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:31:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e959f054e038570919665b44ff4bd9cb2574c5c","tid":1516287,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ab2c589d306eedf6101a2e565808465f47f9a456","tid":1516287,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7287ad5df30888d6d431af5728551e1c79473b70","tid":1516287,"uid":33498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"你班藍屍黑社會小心俾人搞"},{"pid":"4077172064d070727a87c3ebd15555fbc12c3ff6","tid":1516287,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"再Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3157f9baa205a58b32bfec59a7db1120c456dacd","tid":1516287,"uid":46385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T18:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecacc7f969cdb7f81d9acb4e9e07e2b34383fad2","tid":1516287,"uid":23433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"以後見到邊個藍絲老黑打人既 一定要私了<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 犯港人者 實捉到你</span></span>"}]}